data.description: This Turn-Key home is move in ready. Come home to this wonderfully maintained open floor planned home. Built in 2021, this home has 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bathrooms and boasts 1860 square feet of living space. The great room to kitchen combination is perfect for gatherings.     The kitchen is well appointed with beautiful granite countertops and a spacious center island. All kitchen appliances are stainless steel that flow wonderfully with the abundance of cabinetry. The gas stove, microwave and dishwasher are less than three years old. The home’s main floor has laminate flooring throughout, while the upstairs bedrooms and hallways have carpet.   The home’s primary bedroom is spacious with a wonderful walk-in closet, while its bathroom boasts double sinks and a large walk-in shower.   If you have an R.V. or need storage for other toys, the home’s side yard is perfect for your needs. The backyard has a large paver patio and the sprinkler lines have been placed to allow for the installation of spring-time turf.   If you enjoy exercising on scenic walking trials, just head down the street and enjoy the wetlands.
